WEBVTT

00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,900
singer actor Wang Yibo has returned for  
歌手兼演员王一博回归

00:00:01,900 --> 00:00:04,965
for the second season of exploring the unknown with Wang Yibo 
《探索心境·王一博》第二季

00:00:04.966 --> 00:00:07.966
in which he unveils a new identity a rock climber
他在片中展现了一个新的身份攀岩者

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:12.633
produced by the Discovery Channel and co-presented by Tencent Video and Warner Bros
由探索频道制作，腾讯视频、华纳兄弟联合呈现

00:00:12.633 --> 00:00:17.133
the outdoor reality show has been streaming on Tencent Video since November 28
此档户外真人秀自11月28日起在腾讯视频上线

00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:20.100
Guided by Oscar winning director Jimmy Chin
由奥斯卡获奖导演吉米·金指导

00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:22.966
also a professional mountain athlete as his mentor
也是职业山地运动员作为他的导师

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:24.966
and accompanied by James Rider Stroud
由詹姆斯·莱德·斯特劳德陪同

00:00:24.966 --> 00:00:26.900
a highly skilled climbing guide
一位技术高超的登山向导

00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:29.833
Wang embarked on a climbing road trip across North America
王开始了横跨北美的攀岩公路旅行

00:00:29.833 --> 00:00:32.866
traveling more than 1000 kilometers over six weeks
在六周内行驶超过1000公里

00:00:32.900 --> 00:00:36.000
together they explored a wide range of climbing styles
他们一起探索了广泛的攀岩方式

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.500
including sport climbing  traditional climbing
包括运动攀登传统攀登

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:41.700
aid climbing  deep water soloing and big wall climbing
器械（辅助）攀登  深水独攀和大岩壁攀登

00:00:42.400 --> 00:00:43.600
the show's first season
该剧的第一季

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:46.533
which followed Wang as he joined six explorers on expeditions
跟随着王加入了六个探险家的探险

00:00:46.533 --> 00:00:48.666
to six physically extreme destinations
去六个极端的目的地

00:00:48.666 --> 00:00:52.033
received a rating of 9.8 out of 10 on Tencent Video
在腾讯视频收获 9.8 分（满分 10 分）

00:00:52.866 --> 00:00:54.566
Capturing emotional moments of Wang
捕捉王一博的动人瞬间

00:00:54.566 --> 00:00:57.400
and fellow explorers conquering fear and pushing their limits
和探险家们一起征服恐惧挑战极限

00:00:57.400 --> 00:01:01.100
the first season won a Gold Telly at the 46th Annual Telly Awards
第一季在第46届年度电视大奖上获得了金电视奖

00:01:01.100 --> 00:01:04.600
often regarded as the documentary industry's equivalent of the Oscars
通常被视为纪录片业的奥斯卡奖

00:01:04.600 --> 00:01:05.966
according to the producers
根据制片人的说法

00:01:05.966 --> 00:01:07.900
Wang chose rock climbing for the new season
王一博新赛季选择了攀岩

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:10.566
because he enjoys the feeling of ascending upward
因为他很享受向上攀登的感觉

00:01:10.566 --> 00:01:12.166
after several rounds of
几轮之

00:01:12.166 --> 00:01:14.033
discussion with the documentary's creative team
与纪录片创意团队讨论

00:01:14.633 --> 00:01:15.900
to prepare for the season
为赛季做准备

00:01:15.900 --> 00:01:17.500
Wang underwent systematic training
王一博接受了系统的训练

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:19.266
and practiced outdoors with a coach
和教练一起在户外练习

00:01:19.266 --> 00:01:21.566
learning safety knowledge and rope techniques
学习安全知识和绳索技术

00:01:22.133 --> 00:01:23.633
he also proactively studied
他还主动研究

00:01:23.633 --> 00:01:26.100
the differences among various climbing disciplines
不同攀岩学科之间的差异

00:01:26.100 --> 00:01:28.700
such as distinctions in gear usage and Protection methods
例如齿轮使用和保护方法的区别

00:01:28.700 --> 00:01:31.000
between sport climbing and traditional climbing
在运动攀岩和传统攀岩之间
